getic Information & Research)\n  | year = 2012\n  | place = Sandy, Utah\n  | url= http://www.fairmormon.org/perspectives/fair-conferences/2012-fair-conference/2012-joseph-smiths-sexual-polyandry-and-the-emperors-new-clothes-on-closer-inspection-what-do-we-find\n }}.\n*{{Citation\n | last=Harris\n | first=Martin\n | author-link=Martin Harris (Latter Day Saints)\n | title=Mormonism\u2014No. II\n | journal=Tiffany's Monthly\n | volume=5\n | year=1859\n | pages=163\u2013170\n | url= http://en.wikisource.org/w/index.php?title=Tiffany%27s_Monthly/volume_5/Number_4/Mormonism--No._II&oldid=314353\n | issue=4\n }}.\n*{{Citation\n | last=Harris\n | first=Matthew L\n | last2=Bringhurst\n | first2=Newell G\n | title=The Mormon Church and Blacks: A Documentary History\n | year=2015\n | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Pn20CgAAQBAJ\n | isbn=978-0-252-09784-3\n }}.\n\n*{{Citation\n | last=Hill\n | first=Donna\n | title=Joseph Smith: The first Mormon\n | year=1977\n | place=Garden City, New York\n | publisher=Doubleday & Co.\n | isbn=0-385-00804-X\n | url=https://archive.org/details/josephsmithfirst00hill\n }}.\n*{{Citation\n | last=Hill\n | first=Marvin S.\n | authorlink=Marvin S. Hill\n | title=Quest for Refuge: The Mormon Flight from American Pluralism\n | year=1989\n | publisher=Signature Books\n | location=Salt Lake City, Utah\n | url=https://archive.org/details/questforrefugemo00hill\n | isbn=978-0-941214-70-4\n }}.\n*{{cite thesis|degree=M.A.|first=Gordon Frank| last=Hodgins| url=http://scholars.wlu.ca/etd/80/ |title=A comparison of the theology of salvation in the teachings of Martin Luther and Joseph Smith, Jr.|publisher=Wilfrid Laurier University|date=1984}}\n*{{Citation\n | last=Howe\n | first=Eber Dudley\n | author-link=Eber Dudley Howe\n | title=Mormonism Unvailed: Or, A Faithful Account of that Singular Imposition and Delusion, from its Rise to the Present Time\n | place=[[Painesville, Ohio]]\n | publisher=Telegraph Press\n | year=1834\n | url = https://books.goo